Distance<T>, ShortestPath<T>
public class DijkstraShortestPath<T>
extends DijkstraDistance<T>
implements ShortestPath<T>

DijkstraShortestPath calculates distances and shortest paths using Dijkstra's single-source-shortest-path algorithm.

Author:
Joshua O'Madadhain, Tom Nelson converted to jung2, Sabina Sara Pfister - adaptation for Cytoscape
